### 7. **Missing CORS Configuration (CWE-942: Permissive Cross-domain Policy)**
**Severity:** MEDIUM  
**Location:** Global (entire application)

**Issue:** No CORS policy defined. Browser will allow cross-origin requests from any domain.

**Recommended Fix:**
